assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: MGI Tech Co., Ltd. engages in the research, development, production, and sale of DNA sequencing instruments, reagents, and related products for life science research, agriculture, precision medicine, and healthcare markets in China and internationally. Its products include instruments, such as sequencers, and automation and ultrasound systems; library preparation reagents kits, sequencing reagents, and sample treatment solutions, as well as ATOPlex Platform, a massively parallel sequencing (MPS) solution; MegaBOLT bioinformatics analysis accelerator, an NGS-concentrated hardware accelerating system for bioinformatics analysis; and pocket single-cell lab, microbiological detection, sequencing lab, SARS-CoV-2 automated extraction, and population genomics solutions. The company's platforms include genetic sequencing, medical imaging, and laboratory automation. Its solutions are used for forensic, population, and agricultural genomics applications. The company was founded in 2013 and is based in Shenzhen, China. It has additional offices in Wuhan, Qingdao, and Changchun, China; San Jose, California; Dubai, United Arab Emirates; Kobe, Japan; Riga, Latvia; and Hong Kong and Singapore. MGI Tech Co., Ltd. operates as a subsidiary of BGI Group.
